'''''Maria''''' was a [[Lambda-class T-4a shuttle/Legends|''Lambda''-class shuttle]] used by the [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel Alliance]] during the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]].

The ''Maria'' [[Death Star plans delivery|delivered]] the [[Death Star plans/Legends|Death Star plans]], recently acquired by [[AX-235]], to [[Leia Organa Solo/Legends|Leia Organa]] on the [[CR90 corvette/Legends|CR90 corvette]] [[Tantive IV/Legends|''Tantive IV'']]. The transfer was [[Death Star plans delivery|interrupted]] by the [[Imperial-class Star Destroyer/Legends|''Imperial''-class Star Destroyer]] ''[[Immortal/Legends|Immortal]]'' which launched several [[Alpha-class Xg-1 Star Wing/Legends|Assault Gunboats]] before jumping into [[Hyperspace/Legends|hyperspace]]. However, the Imperial fighters were destroyed by Rebel [[T-65 X-wing starfighter/Legends|X-wings]], led by [[Keyan Farlander/Legends|Keyan Farlander]], and the ''Maria'' was able to escape after successfully transferring the plans.

